{"id": "art-1372", "label": "Art. 1372", "title": "Art. 1372", "slug": "art-1372", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1892992734\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2251\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1892992734\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 137<sup>2</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1269951564\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2250\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1269951564\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În caz de <span class=SpellE>vacan&#355;&#259;</span> a\nunuia sau a mai multor posturi de administrator, dac&#259; prin actul\nconstitutiv nu se dispune altfel, consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\nprocedeaz&#259; la numirea unor administratori provizorii, pân&#259; la\nîntrunirea adun&#259;rii generale ordinare a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_199517422\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2249\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_199517422\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; <span class=SpellE>vacan&#355;a</span>\nprev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1) determin&#259; sc&#259;derea num&#259;rului\nadministratorilor sub minimul legal, administratorii <span class=SpellE>r&#259;ma&#351;i</span>\nconvoac&#259; de îndat&#259; adunarea general&#259; ordinar&#259; a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, pentru a completa num&#259;rul de membri\nai consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1611735225\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2248\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1611735225\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul în care administratorii nu <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\nîndeplinesc <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ia</span> de a convoca adunarea\ngeneral&#259;, orice parte interesat&#259; se poate adresa <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span>\npentru a desemna persoana îns&#259;rcinat&#259; cu convocarea adun&#259;rii\ngenerale ordinare a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, care s&#259;\nfac&#259; numirile necesare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1613512212\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2247\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1613512212\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Când este un singur administrator <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nacesta vrea s&#259; <span class=SpellE>renun&#355;e</span> la mandat, el va\ntrebui s&#259; convoace adunarea general&#259; ordinar&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_40832067\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2246\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_40832067\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În caz de deces sau de imposibilitate fizic&#259; de\nexercitare a <span class=SpellE>func&#355;iei</span> de administrator unic,\nnumirea provizorie se va face de c&#259;tre cenzori, îns&#259; adunarea\ngeneral&#259; ordinar&#259; va fi convocat&#259; de <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span>\npentru numirea definitiv&#259; a administratorului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_796033250\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2245\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_796033250\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)În cazul în care societatea nu are cenzori, orice <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span> se poate adresa <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span>\ncare autorizeaz&#259; convocarea adun&#259;rii generale de c&#259;tre <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarul</span> care a formulat cererea sau de c&#259;tre\nalt <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span>. Prin <span class=SpellE>aceea&#351;i</span>\nhot&#259;râre, <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span> aprob&#259; ordinea de\nzi, <span class=SpellE>stabile&#351;te</span> data de <span class=SpellE>referin&#355;&#259;</span>\nprev&#259;zut&#259; de art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>123 alin. (2)</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, data <span class=SpellE>&#355;inerii</span> adun&#259;rii\ngenerale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dintre <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span>,\npersoana care o va prezida.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}